A set of utilities for linux.

linux.mounts() gives an object containing details pertaining to 
the current mounted filesystems.

linux.ps() gives an object with details on all processes on the
system.

linux.ps.pid( pidnum ) gives an object with details pertaining
to pid pidnum.

linux.acpi.batteries() gives an object containing details of all
batteries.

linux.acpi.battery( batName ) gives an object containing details
of battery batName.

linux.sysctl() gives an object with getter and setter functions
to use. See test.js for details.
